						<p><div class="item">
<h2><a class="listing" style="link" href="/en/Dossiers/CTA-and-S-T/Fellowships-grants-calls/Postgraduate-scholarships-for-Loughborough-University-UK" title="Postgraduate scholarships for Loughborough University, UK " alt="link">Postgraduate scholarships for Loughborough University, UK </a></h2>

	
					<p>Loughborough University offers full-fee scholarships for international full-time taught postgraduate students permanently living in Africa. The scholarships cover 100% of the course fees for your chosen postgraduate taught course for one year, travel and maintenance costs will need to be financed through other sources. Students may only apply for the scholarship after an offer for a place at Loughborough University has been made. <b>The deadline for application is the 30th of April 2010.</b></p>
							<p><span class="date">21/12/2009</span></p>
	<div class="cnt">
	<a class="link" href="/en/Dossiers/CTA-and-S-T/Fellowships-grants-calls/Postgraduate-scholarships-for-Loughborough-University-UK">Read more...</a>
