						<p><div class="item">
<h2><a class="listing" style="link" href="/en/Dossiers/CTA-and-S-T/Fellowships-grants-calls/MA-scholarship-for-course-in-environmental-sciences-policy-and-management" title="MA scholarship for course in environmental sciences, policy and management" alt="link">MA scholarship for course in environmental sciences, policy and management</a></h2>

	
					<p>The Masters Course in Environmental Sciences, Policy and Management Scholarships (MESPOM) are provided by the 








 




  
  

	
	<a href="/var/knowledge/storage/images/media/images/logos/mespom/290303-1-eng-GB/Mespom.jpg" rel="lightbox[]" >	
	  </a>
	
		
			
	
  	






	 
  





	EU. MESPOM prepares students for developing integrated solutions to environmental challenges, especially in an international context. The EC's Erasmus Mundus programme provides scholarships to outstanding students from countries outside the EU to attend MESPOM and to scholars to participate in teaching and research. <b>The deadline for MESPOM applications is the 1st of April 2010. </b>Please note that there are many other courses for which scholarships are offered (http://eacea.ec.europa.eu/erasmus_mundus/results_compendia/selected_projects_action_1_master_courses_en.php).</p>
							<p><span class="date">21/12/2009</span></p>
	<div class="cnt">
	<a class="link" href="/en/Dossiers/CTA-and-S-T/Fellowships-grants-calls/MA-scholarship-for-course-in-environmental-sciences-policy-and-management">Read more...</a>
