						<p><div class="item">
<h2><a class="listing" style="link" href="/en/Dossiers/CTA-and-S-T/Fellowships-grants-calls/University-of-Ghent-master-course-scholarships" title="University of Ghent master course scholarships " alt="link">University of Ghent master course scholarships </a></h2>

	
					<p>The University of Ghent will award a maximum of 10 scholarships annually to students from developing countries.<b> </b>Students who already have official entry into the University of Ghent may hand in their application before the 1st of March 2010. The master scholarships are awarded for the duration of the studies, aiming at the delivery of a Ghent University diploma after a maximum of 2 years of study. The scholarship is in principle paid for the total duration of the studies. <b>The deadline for applications is the 23rd of December 2009</b></p>
							<p><span class="date">21/12/2009</span></p>
	<div class="cnt">
	<a class="link" href="/en/Dossiers/CTA-and-S-T/Fellowships-grants-calls/University-of-Ghent-master-course-scholarships">Read more...</a>
